<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink366">
<l>aṉṉāy vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉaiyeṉ ṟōḻi</l>
<l>pacantaṉaḷ periteṉac civanta kaṇṇai</l>
<l>koṉṉē kaṭavuti yāyi ṉeṉṉatūu</l>
<l>maṟiya vākumō maṟṟē</l>
<l>muṟiyiṇark kōṅkam payanta māṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Mother, may you live long! Listen, mother! </l>
<l>If you, whose eyes reddened [because of anger], uselessly urge me,</l>
<l>saying that my friend has become pale,</l>
<l>is there [at least] a little to be known?</l>
<l>Changes are caused by the Kōṇkam tree with blossoming flowers!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
